description: Retrieves a list that describes the streaming sessions for a specified pool.

nested_items.name: AuthenticationType
nested_items.description: The authentication method. The user is authenticated using a WorkSpaces Pools URL (API) or SAML 2.0 federation (SAML).

nested_items.name: ConnectionState
nested_items.description: Specifies whether a user is connected to the pool session.

nested_items.name: InstanceId
nested_items.description: The identifier for the instance hosting the session.

nested_items.name: ExpirationTime
nested_items.description: The time that the pool session ended.

nested_items.name: NetworkAccessConfiguration
nested_items.description: Describes the network details of the pool.

nested_items.name: EniPrivateIpAddress
nested_items.description: The private IP address of the elastic network interface that is attached to instances in your VPC.

nested_items.name: EniId
nested_items.description: The resource identifier of the elastic network interface that is attached to instances in your VPC. All network interfaces have the eni-xxxxxxxx resource identifier.

nested_items.name: StartTime
nested_items.description: The time that the pool sission started.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: If you received a NextToken from a previous call that was paginated, provide this token to receive the next set of results.
